title: Internet Crime Perpetrators Per Capita by State, 2007
name: Internet Crime Perpetrators Per Capita by State, 2007
description:
This data reports Internet crime perpetrators per capita (per 100,000 people) by State for 2007.

The data was extracted from the 2007 Internet Crime Report prepared by The National White Collar Crime Center, the Bureau of Justice Assistance, FBI. Further details provided in the link to the report in the URL below.
